## 3. YAML Frontmatter Specification

All wiki pages **must** include YAML frontmatter:

```yaml
---
title: 页面标题（与 H1 一致）
slug: english-slug
type: source | entity | concept | synthesis
date: YYYY-MM-DD
updated: YYYY-MM-DD
tags: [标签1, 标签2, 标签3]
sources: [sources/相关摘要1, sources/相关摘要2]
related: [entities/实体页, concepts/概念页, synthesis/综合页]
aliases: [别名1, 别名2]           # optional
severity: high | medium | low     # optional, pain-point pages only
frequency: high | medium | low    # optional, pain-point pages only
---
```

**Required fields**: `title`, `slug`, `type`, `date`, `updated`, `tags`, `sources`, `related`
**Optional fields**: `aliases`, `severity`, `frequency`

